title: 'America's Next Top Model' leaving the runway in December
text:
> Entertainment 'America's Next Top Model' leaving the runway in December FILE - In this July 28, 2015 file photo,Tyra Banks attends the "America's Next Top Model" Cycle 22 Premiere Party at Greystone Manor, in Los Angeles. The CW reality competition series will wrap in Dec. 2015 with the current season's finale. Banks, the show's host and executive producer, just launched the syndicated daytime talk show "FABLife." (Photo by Paul A. Hebert/Invision/AP, File) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
